Nobody warned me how different Vietnamese coffee tastes. They use Robusta and it has such a how do I put it... peculiar taste?..I tried the Phin coffee the iced latte way (no sugar) and I did not like it.. Like noooo! The only way I could consume it is if it's sweetened 🥲 which is why I decided to stick with Coconut Coffee coz it's sweet. Boy I missed Arabica sm there 🫶🏻🥹
